{{! Rogue Trader Bleeding Card - Modern Design }}
<div class="wh40k-chat">
    <div class="wh40k-roll-card">
        {{! Header }}
        <div class="wh40k-roll-card__header">
            <div class="wh40k-roll-card__actor">{{actor.name}}</div>
            <h2 class="wh40k-roll-card__title">Bleeding!</h2>
            <div class="wh40k-roll-card__subtitle">Critical Condition</div>
        </div>

        {{! Body }}
        <div class="wh40k-roll-card__body">
            <div class="wh40k-roll-card__row">
                <span class="wh40k-roll-card__label">Fatigue</span>
                <span class="wh40k-roll-card__value">{{system.fatigue.value}} / {{system.fatigue.max}}</span>
            </div>

            <div class="wh40k-roll-card__text">
                <p>Once per round as a Free Action, the character (or another who can reach them) can attempt a
                    <strong>Difficult (–10) Medicae</strong>
                    test to remove this condition.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="wh40k-roll-card__damage">
                <div class="wh40k-roll-card__damage-header">
                    <span class="wh40k-roll-card__damage-title">Fatigue</span>
                </div>
                <div class="wh40k-roll-card__damage-value">+1</div>
                <div class="wh40k-roll-card__damage-type">Blood Loss</div>
            </div>

            <div class="wh40k-roll-card__controls">
                <button
                    class="wh40k-roll-card__btn wh40k-roll-card__btn--damage roll-control__apply-damage"
                    data-uuid="{{actor.uuid}}"
                    data-damage="0"
                    data-fatigue="1"
                >
                    <span class="material-icons">api</span>
                    <span>Apply Fatigue</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>